         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="Prototype orders are used to manage orders for prototypes that a company manufactures or sells. These orders may involve special handling and have different pricing or delivery terms compared to regular orders. This allows to track and manage the production and delivery of prototype products separately from the regular orders"/>
